responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "EF075E3B406087754B0B0B98458A2066", "Spindle Spider Comes from yonder. Comes to places yesterday. Crawl upon your spindle spandle. Web arouser no handle for thee. Come down your web of agony. From nether ether lost is thee. Climmber Clamber a web canopy.")
